        "body": "<p>Approximately, something like that :<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>    int numberOfButtons = getIntent().getExtras().getInt(\"numberOfButtons\", 0);\n    for (int i = 1; i &lt;= numberOfButtons; ++i)\n    {\n        Button btn = new Button(this);\n        btn.setText(\"Button n° \" + i);\n\n        // YOUR_WIDGET_THAT_WILL_CONTAIN_YOUr_BUTTONS.addView(btn);\n\n    }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
